t home for researchers and students whose interests span multiple disciplines.  See the program pages for more information on the different areas of concentration within our department.          Programs    Back to main content           Mathematics    Mathematical Computer Science    Mathematics Education     Contact    Advising    FAQ    Elementary Education     Bachelor of Arts     Math 140 & 141    Math Concentration      Master of Science     Courses        Secondary Education     Bachelor of Science    Master of Science     MST for Licensed Teachers    MST + License        Doctoral Program      Statistics     Statistics Consulting @ UIC                     UIC Logo         College of  Liberal Arts  And  Sciences           MSCS Quick Links    JSTOR (via proxy)    Front for the arXiv    Numdam    MathSciNet (via proxy)    Naxos Music Library (via proxy)         Contact   Department of Mathematics, Statistics, and Computer Science  851 S. Morgan Street ,322 Science and Engineering Offices (M/C 249) Chicago, IL 60607-7045  Phone: (312) 996-3041  Fax: (312) 996-1491  webmaster@math.uic.edu        Social Media Accounts             UIC.edu links   UIC.edu  Academic Calendar  Athletics  Campus Directory  Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Event Calendar  Job Openings  Library  Maps  UIC Safe Mobile App  UIC Today  UI Health  Veterans Affairs        Powered by Red 2.38.0  © 2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois |  Privacy Statement    Campuses   University of Illinois System  Urbana-Champaign  Springfield      Cookie Settings                   